Title	:	 Purchase Zone : E-commerce Web Application	

Platform	:	 React ,Java J2EE(SpringBoot) ,MySQL

Duration	:	 1 Month

Description	:	We developed a robust and user-friendly eCommerce platform. Some of the core features include a seamless user experience,
              user authentication and authorization, order tracking, and the Razorpay payment gateway to make secure payments during checkout.
              Additionally, we implemented comprehensive order summary functionality, allowing users to review their orders before confirming payment.
              And lastly, an efficient admin dashboard for managing products and orders. This entire application is developed using React as the user interface
              and Java J2EE Spring Boot as the backend, with MySql as a database.	
 	 	 	 
